OL,3,CMan arrested after man found stabbed
OL,4,Cto death in garden
OL,6,FA man has been arrested on suspicion
OL,7,Fof murder after a body was found at
OL,8,Fthe rear of a garden.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to a
OL,11,Fproperty in Filton, near Bristol, in
OL,12,Fthe early hours of, Thursday 9 April,
OL,13,Fafter a man in his 20s was found with
OL,14,Fseveral stab wounds. He was pronounced
OL,15,Fdead at the scene.
OL,17,FAnother man, also in his 20s, was
OL,18,Farrested on suspicion of murder on,
OL,19,FSunday 12 April.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
