PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1776010270
OL,3,CMan arrested after man found stabbed
OL,4,Cto death in garden
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector Lucy
OL,7,FEdgeworth, of Avon and Somerset
OL,8,FPolice, said: "The victim's family are
OL,9,Faware of the arrest and our thoughts
OL,10,Fare with them following their
OL,11,Fdevastating loss.
OL,13,F"Out of respect to his family, we
OL,14,Fwould ask people not to speculate on
OL,15,Fthe man's identity, or the wider
OL,16,Fcircumstances around his death.
OL,18,F"They are continuing to privately
OL,19,Fgrieve at this time, and we would ask
OL,20,Fthat their privacy is respected."
OL,26,@pD@OOUuD@AOUzD@AOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
