OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1776010270
OL,3,CMan arrested after man found stabbed
OL,4,Cto death in garden
OL,6,FShe said the formal identification
OL,7,Fprocess has not yet been completed.
OL,9,FA spokesman for Avon and Somerset
OL,10,FPolice said a forensic post-mortem
OL,11,Fexamination has indicated the man died
OL,12,Fafter sustaining a "number of stab
OL,13,Fwounds".
OL,15,FHe was found at the rear of a garden
OL,16,Fin Cleve Road, Filton, on Thursday,
OL,17,Fnear a pathway running behind the
OL,18,Fhouses.
OL,20,FIt is believed he had died several
OL,21,Fhours earlier on Wednesday 8 April.
OL,26,@tD@TOUuD@GO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
