FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1776010270
OL,3,CMan arrested after man found stabbed
OL,4,Cto death in garden
OL,6,FMs Edgeworth added: "A huge amount of
OL,7,Fwork has been carried out by the
OL,8,Finvestigation team and specialist
OL,9,Fofficers in recent days.
OL,11,F"This includes reviewing many hours of
OL,12,FCCTV footage, carrying out forensic
OL,13,Fenquiries at the scene, conducting
OL,14,Fdetailed searches of the local area
OL,15,Fand speaking to potential witnesses.
OL,17,F"This has led to an arrest being made
OL,18,Fand the man remains in custody where
OL,19,Fhe will be questioned under caution."
OL,26,@nD@UOUsD@AOUyD@AOU{D@eO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
